Our thoughts and love are always with you
Your loving wife Maraki and family

[Right]
IN LOVING MEMORY
MARAKI HILLOCK
(formerly GRIMSHAW nee DIAMANTAKI)
BORN IN SYROS, GREECE 1926 DIED 01/03/2012
AGED 86

OUR THOUGHTS AND LOVE ARE ALWAYS WITH YOU
YOUR LOVING FAMILY"¾
